_templates.javolution.util

Class FastList.Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • _templates.javolution.util.FastList.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, FastCollection.Record
    Enclosing class:
    FastList

    public static class FastList.Node
extends java.lang.Object
implements FastCollection.Record, Serializable
    This class represents a FastList node; it allows for direct iteration over the list values. Custom FastList may use a derived implementation. For example:[code] static class MyList extends FastList { protected MyNode newNode() { return new MyNode(); } class MyNode extends Node { X xxx; // Additional node field (e.g. cross references). } }[/code]
